---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const base = '/tradfi-onchain';
---

<Layout title="Investment Banking — Tokenized Issuance">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pt-24 pb-12">
    <p class="text-cyan-400 text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase mb-4">
      <span class="lang-en">Investment Banking</span><span class="lang-zh">投資銀行</span>
    </p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight mb-6">
      <span class="lang-en">How ECM/DCM Teams Are Exploring<br/>Tokenized Issuance</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">ECM/DCM團隊如何<br/>探索代幣化發行</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-zinc-400 max-w-3xl">
      <span class="lang-en">Goldman Sachs, HSBC, and the European Investment Bank have already executed tokenized bond issuances. The NYSE is partnering with Securitize for 24/7 tokenized securities trading. This is not a pilot — it's primary market infrastructure being rebuilt onchain.</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">Goldman Sachs、HSBC同歐洲投資銀行已經完成代幣化債券發行。NYSE正同Securitize合作建立24/7代幣化證券交易。呢個唔係pilot — 係primary market infrastructure喺chain上重建。</span>
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- The Shift -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">The Shift: Primary Issuance Moving Onchain</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">轉變：一級發行遷移上鏈</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p>
          <span class="lang-en">Traditional bond issuance requires coordination between issuer, underwriter, custodian, clearing house, and registrar — a process that typically takes 5-14 days from pricing to settlement. Tokenized issuance collapses this into a single onchain transaction with instant settlement, programmable compliance, and 24/7 secondary market access.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">傳統債券發行需要發行人、承銷商、託管人、結算所同登記機構之間的協調 — 從定價到結算通常需要5-14天。代幣化發行將此壓縮為單個鏈上交易，實現即時結算、可編程合規同24/7二級市場准入。</span>
        </p>
        <p>
          <span class="lang-en">The cost savings are significant. McKinsey estimates that tokenized bond issuance can reduce operational costs by 30-50% through elimination of intermediary reconciliation, automated coupon payments, and instant cross-border settlement.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">成本節省顯著。麥肯錫估計，代幣化債券發行可通過消除中介對賬、自動化票息支付及即時跨境結算，降低運營成本30-50%。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Live Deals -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Live Deals: Who Is Doing This</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">實際案例：誰在做</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">Goldman Sachs GS DAP</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">DCM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Platform:</span><span class="lang-zh">平台：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">GS DAP (Digital Asset Platform) — private blockchain built for institutional bond issuance.</span><span class="lang-zh">GS DAP (Digital Asset Platform) — 專為機構債券發行而建的私有鏈。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Key deal:</span><span class="lang-zh">重要交易：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">European Investment Bank (EIB) EUR 100M digital bond — the first major supranational tokenized issuance.</span><span class="lang-zh">歐洲投資銀行（EIB）EUR 100M digital bond — 首個大型超國家機構代幣化發行。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Roadmap:</span><span class="lang-zh">路線圖：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Plans to spin out GS DAP as an independent entity by mid-2026, signaling this is a permanent business line, not an experiment.</span><span class="lang-zh">計劃於2026年中將GS DAP分拆為獨立實體，表明這是永久業務線，而非實驗。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">HSBC Orion</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">DCM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Platform:</span><span class="lang-zh">平台：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Orion — institutional-grade tokenization platform for bond issuance and settlement.</span><span class="lang-zh">Orion — 機構級代幣化平台，用於債券發行和結算。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Key deal:</span><span class="lang-zh">重要交易：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong Government tokenized green bond — 3rd issuance, cumulative HK$10B. Settled entirely through Orion.</span><span class="lang-zh">香港政府代幣化綠色債券 — 第3次發行，累計HK$100億。全部通過Orion結算。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Scale:</span><span class="lang-zh">規模：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Also handling tokenized deposits globally. Orion is not a side project — it's becoming core infrastructure.</span><span class="lang-zh">同時處理全球代幣化存款。Orion不是副項目 — 正成為核心基礎設施。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">NYSE × Securitize</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">ECM</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium">MOU:</span> <span class="lang-en">NYSE signed a memorandum of understanding with Securitize, the leading tokenization platform (which also partners with BlackRock BUIDL).</span><span class="lang-zh">NYSE同Securitize（領先代幣化平台，亦係BlackRock BUIDL嘅合作夥伴）簽署諒解備忘錄。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Goal:</span><span class="lang-zh">目標：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Build a 24/7 tokenized securities trading platform. This would extend NYSE's reach beyond traditional trading hours.</span><span class="lang-zh">建立24/7代幣化證券交易平台。這將把NYSE的覆蓋範圍延伸至傳統交易時段之外。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Implication:</span><span class="lang-zh">影響：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">ECM teams should watch this closely — the primary listing paradigm may shift within 3-5 years.</span><span class="lang-zh">ECM團隊應密切關注 — 一級上市範式可能在3-5年內改變。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white">JP Morgan Kinexys</h3>
          <span class="text-xs text-cyan-400 bg-cyan-500/10 px-2.5 py-1 rounded-full">Settlement</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Scale:</span><span class="lang-zh">規模：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">$1.5T+ total transactions processed. $2B+ daily intraday repo volume.</span><span class="lang-zh">已處理交易總額超$1.5T。日均回購量超$2B。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Use cases:</span><span class="lang-zh">應用場景：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">Onchain FX settlement, intraday repo, cross-border payments — the plumbing that makes capital markets work.</span><span class="lang-zh">鏈上外匯結算、日內回購、跨境支付 — 令資本市場運作的管道。</span></p>
          <p><span class="text-white font-medium"><span class="lang-en">Signal:</span><span class="lang-zh">信號：</span></span> <span class="lang-en">When the world's largest bank processes $1.5T+ through blockchain, it's no longer experimental.</span><span class="lang-zh">當全球最大銀行通過區塊鏈處理超$1.5T，這已不再是實驗。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Changes for IB -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">What Changes for Investment Banking Teams</span>
      <span class="lang-zh">投資銀行團隊的變化</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">DCM</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Bond Issuance</span><span class="lang-zh">債券發行</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="lang-en">Tokenized bonds settle instantly instead of T+2. Coupon payments are automated via smart contracts. Investors can access the secondary market 24/7.</span><span class="lang-zh">代幣化債券即時結算，取代T+2。票息支付通過智能合約自動化。投資者可24/7進入二級市場。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en">Advisory opportunity: help issuers evaluate tokenized vs traditional issuance. Structuring tokenized tranches alongside traditional ones.</span><span class="lang-zh">顧問機會：幫助發行人評估代幣化與傳統發行。在傳統發行旁邊構建代幣化tranche。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">ECM</p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Securities Trading</span><span class="lang-zh">證券交易</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="lang-en">NYSE × Securitize MOU points toward 24/7 tokenized equity trading. This may eventually blur the line between IPO and token launch.</span><span class="lang-zh">NYSE × Securitize MOU指向24/7代幣化股權交易。這最終可能模糊IPO和代幣發行之間的界限。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en">Fractional ownership unlocks smaller ticket sizes. Global investors can participate without local brokerage accounts.</span><span class="lang-zh">碎片化所有權解鎖更小的投資額度。全球投資者無需本地券商賬戶即可參與。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-cyan-400 font-medium mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Structured Products</span><span class="lang-zh">結構化產品</span>
        </p>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-3">
          <span class="lang-en">Programmable Finance</span><span class="lang-zh">可編程金融</span>
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <p><span class="lang-en">Smart contracts can automate coupon calculations, waterfall distributions, and compliance checks. DBS Singapore is already issuing tokenized structured notes on Ethereum.</span><span class="lang-zh">智能合約可自動化票息計算、瀑布式分配及合規檢查。DBS Singapore已在Ethereum上發行代幣化結構性票據。</span></p>
          <p><span class="lang-en">Composability means structured products can be built on top of tokenized treasuries (BlackRock BUIDL as collateral).</span><span class="lang-zh">可組合性意味著結構化產品可建立在代幣化美債之上（BlackRock BUIDL作抵押品）。</span></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HK Context -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-16">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
      <span class="lang-en">Hong Kong Context</span><span class="lang-zh">香港背景</span>
    </h2>
    <div class="bg-zinc-900/50 border border-zinc-800/50 rounded-xl p-8">
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        <p><span class="lang-en">Hong Kong is actively embracing tokenized issuance at the government level. The HK Government's tokenized green bond program (cumulative HK$10B, settled via HSBC Orion) is one of the largest sovereign tokenized bond programs globally.</span><span class="lang-zh">香港正在政府層面積極擁抱代幣化發行。港府代幣化綠色債券計劃（累計HK$100億，經HSBC Orion結算）是全球最大的主權代幣化債券計劃之一。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">With 12 licensed VATPs, a stablecoin ordinance in place, and upcoming VA dealer/custodian licensing, HK is building the full regulatory stack for tokenized capital markets.</span><span class="lang-zh">擁有12間持牌VATP、穩定幣條例已實施、以及即將推出的VA交易商/託管人牌照，香港正在構建代幣化資本市場的完整監管框架。</span></p>
        <p><span class="lang-en">For IB teams in Hong Kong: the question is no longer "will tokenized issuance happen?" but "how do we position our team for the transition?"</span><span class="lang-zh">對於香港的IB團隊：問題不再是「代幣化發行會否發生？」而是「我們如何為轉型做好準備？」</span></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom CTA -->
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 pb-24">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-950/30 to-zinc-900/50 border border-green-900/30 rounded-xl p-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">
          <span class="lang-en">Want to discuss how this applies to your team?</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">想討論這如何應用到你的團隊？</span>
        </h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          <span class="lang-en">We help finance professionals navigate the transition to onchain markets.</span>
          <span class="lang-zh">我們幫助金融從業者應對向鏈上市場的過渡。</span>
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="https://wa.me/85256171671" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 bg-green-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-green-400 transition-colors whitespace-nowrap">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"/></svg>
        WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 flex gap-4">
      <a href={`${base}/apply/asset-management`} class="text-sm text-zinc-500 hover:text-white transition-colors">
        <span class="lang-en">Next: Asset Management →</span><span class="lang-zh">下一篇：資產管理 →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
